item.dc:creator: @purestmage74 purestmage74
item.description:
@purestmage74 wrote:

lol at the people saying ‘z0mg it closes fast!@ help’…

learn .bat files (batch files).
They take commands inside of the file.
One command (common with rsps…) left at the bottom of the file is ‘exit’.

So anything above that (Being executed), if a error occurs, it will just dump that line, move to the final phrase, which is iether ‘exit’ or ‘pause’.

If you’d like to see what caused the .bat file error.
simply add a pause… =]

@echo off
@color 0a
@title Compiling Elites Chronicles PT.2

:main
cls
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_24\bin\javac" -classpath deps/log4j-1.2.15.jar;deps/jython.jar;deps/xstream.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/poi.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar -d bin src\server\event\*.java src\server\model\items\*.java src\server\model\minigames\*.java src\server\model\npcs\*.java src\server\model\objects\*.java src\server\model\players\*.java src\server\model\players\skills\*.java src\server\model\players\packets\*.java src\server\model\shops\*.java src\server\net\*.java src\server\task\*.java src\server\util\*.java src\server\world\*.java src\server\util\log\*.java src\server\*.java src\server\world\map\*.java
pause
goto main

And lol @ the 9 year olds programming this ‘if you host this server, ill find you, ill charge you money’.
I already changed the server name, changed and removed all the dumbass programming in 1 file so far.
Anyways, I be gettin mad at kids postin shit like that in their server.
How the fuck do you think we got ‘Runescape Private Servers’, it’s from people decompiling (illegally), and reverse engineering their shit.

So don’t complain if your little ‘leech of a leech, of another leech’ gets leeched again…
You’re helping this community in someway.
